headline: Costco earnings, Fedspeak, pending home sales: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime anchors Julie Hyman and Josh Lipton preview the top market headlines and economic data expected to hit Wall Street tomorrow, Thursday, May 29, including earnings results from company's like Costco Wholesale (COST), Dell Technologies (DELL), The Gap (GAP), Marvell Technology (MRVL), and Li Auto (LI); the latest commentary from several Federal Reserve officials; and the most recent data print on pending home sales in the US. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.
